205
00:13:38,048 --> 00:13:39,413
Abu, we need a new car.

206
00:13:39,450 --> 00:13:41,714
But our bank account was empty.

207
00:13:41,752 --> 00:13:44,277
And retire this magnificent chariot?

208
00:13:44,321 --> 00:13:45,549
Nonsense.

209
00:13:45,589 --> 00:13:48,786
These new-money scoundrels
are ruining the place.

210
00:13:49,960 --> 00:13:51,621
Your Bina madam's waiting.

211
