or something.

248
00:15:16,083 --> 00:15:17,846
But, Chan, what about
your Mr. Bond?

249
00:15:17,884 --> 00:15:20,352
Oh, please.
Bond?

250
00:15:20,387 --> 00:15:22,821
I'd drop him in a second
for Mr. Big.

251
00:15:22,856 --> 00:15:25,324
All I want is a loft in SoHo,

252
00:15:25,359 --> 00:15:26,951
