253
00:15:26,994 --> 00:15:31,897
and a pair of big,
fake American boobs.

254
00:15:31,932 --> 00:15:33,866
What? Is that too much to ask?

255
00:15:33,900 --> 00:15:35,390
Not at all.

256
00:15:35,435 --> 00:15:37,097
God bless America.

257
00:15:38,639 --> 00:15:41,506
God bless America, indeed.

258
00:15:41,542 --> 00:15:44,568
